::VorbIss::

"Well then," replied VorbIss, "I'm sorry I overestimated you." VorbIss 
smirked. "This shuttle is owned by a faction called The Alliance, who wanted 
me to join them. I am, I expect, about to leave in it to meet them. They may 
well help you as well."
